OverHistory.UPDCommentry:
BACK TO BACK WICKETS  Shreyanka Patil bowling to Tahlia McGrath, good length ball, pitching on off stump, Tahlia McGrath is rapped on the back pad. With no saving grace from technology, Australia now lose their review alongside the key wicket.

(Australia Women 216 Runs for 4 wickets)
